# Ambimax PHP {{ php.version }}-{{ distro }} Dockerimage

New generation of php containers. All settings can be adjusted on the fly by ENV variables.

Currently supported Frameworks and Apps:

- Symfony
- Shopware 6
- Open Mage / Magento 1
- Magento 2

